description: 803 E 5th St., South Boston – Refined Living by Expert Craftsmen. Welcome to this fully renovated home on a quiet street just minutes from the beach, Castle Island, and South Boston’s best restaurants. Designed by expert builders with a mastery of finish carpentry, this home is filled with details that impress—crown molding, coffered ceilings, built-ins, custom mantle, and an elegant gas fireplace anchoring the living space. The chef’s kitchen features Thermador appliances, custom cabinetry, and a seamless flow, perfect for entertaining. Enjoy the deck with sunrise skies off a second living space, or a cookout on your private patio. A dedicated home office provides modern convenience, while thoughtful storage adds everyday ease. With its prime location, meticulous craftsmanship, and upscale finishes, 803 E 5th offers the perfect blend of charm and sophistication in one of Boston’s most desirable neighborhoods. Schedule your private tour today and discover your South Boston retreat.
